title: Man In Manual Wheelchair Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a person using a manual wheelchair, signifying accessibility, independence, disability, or mobility challenges.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the man in manual wheelchair emoji with a dark skin tone is depicted with a determined and engaged expression, his form rendered with Apple's signature smooth gradients and realistic lighting. The wheelchair itself is detailed with soft, rounded spokes and a comfortable-looking seat, highlighting accessibility and independence. This emoji from Apple's inclusive collection is a powerful symbol of representation, capability, and overcoming challenges.
